snippet.title: Pyoro 64 - 2018 Nintendo 64 Game (Real N64 Capture)
snippet.description:
Someone ported the Pyoro minigame from WarioWare into the N64, because we live in magical times. Playing in "hard mode" (meaning with a busted joystick) but still figured out how to cheese the game to get to 10,000 points and unlock Pyoro 2 (skip to 14:47 to see that). 

Download this game for free here: https://www.reddit.com/r/N64Homebrew/comments/a9ipog/pyoro64/

(Captured through an Avermedia Game Capture HD II, a RetroTink 2X, and an RGB-modded Nintendo 64 with HD Retrovision cables.)
